| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4091 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 64fd32ec-3ecb-5b38-9cab-e3d1b9c54434"
